## Review Criteria (from CLAUDE.md)

- Thread safety (threading.Lock, no blocking I/O in hot path)
- Memory bounds (4-8 GB Jetson shared RAM)
- Main loop sustains >= 5 FPS
- Fail-safe behavior (graceful degradation, not crashes)
- Input validation at system boundaries
- Bearer token auth on control endpoints
- All tunables in config.ini
- Python 3.10+ type hints, dataclasses

